Title: Added more link views for Host Groups (Summary)
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p6
Date: 1572535913

The view Host Groups (Summary) did not have any links in the shown data,
that would display more details. With this change, all statistics are now
linked to such a more detailed view.
